"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Spanish passengers are the first to leave the MV Hondius after an outbreak where three people died and several got sick.\",            \"english_title\": \"Spanish Passengers Leave Ship\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los pasajeros espa\u00f1oles son los primeros en salir del MV Hondius despu\u00e9s de un brote donde murieron tres personas y varias se enfermaron.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Pasajeros espa\u00f1oles salen del barco\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Russian leader sees a chance for talks with Ukraine but criticizes the West for supporting President Zelensky.\",            \"english_title\": \"Russian Leader Seeks Talks\",            \"translated_version\": \"El l\u00edder ruso ve una oportunidad para hablar con Ucrania pero critica a Occidente por apoyar al Presidente Zelensky.\",            \"translated_title\": \"L\u00edder ruso busca hablar\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Officials are looking into what caused the explosion at a popular marina in southern Florida.\",            \"english_title\": \"Explosion in Florida Marina\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los oficiales est\u00e1n investigando qu\u00e9 caus\u00f3 la explosi\u00f3n en una marina popular en el sur de Florida.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Explosi\u00f3n en marina de Florida\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Nearly a month ago, P\u00e9ter Magyar led his Tisza party to a big win, ending 16 years of rule by Viktor Orb\u00e1n.\",            \"english_title\": \"P\u00e9ter Magyar's Big Win\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hace casi un mes, P\u00e9ter Magyar llev\u00f3 a su partido Tisza a una gran victoria, terminando 16 a\u00f1os de gobierno de Viktor Orb\u00e1n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Gran victoria de P\u00e9ter Magyar\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Israel and Hezbollah continue to exchange fire even though a ceasefire was announced last month.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israel and Hezbollah Conflict\",            \"translated_version\": \"Israel y Hezbollah siguen intercambiando disparos aunque se anunci\u00f3 un alto el fuego el mes pasado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Conflicto entre Israel y Hezbollah\"        }    ]}"